<ResourceLayout 
  name="Twilight Psychology Location"
  description="Find our office locations and hours"
>
  <h2>Welcome to Our Locations Page</h2>
  <p>
    Explore our office locations and find the one that is most convenient for you. We are committed to providing accessible and high-quality care to all our clients.
  </p>

  <h2>Office Hours</h2>
  <p>
    Our office hours are designed to accommodate the needs of our clients. Please check the specific location for detailed hours of operation.
  </p>

  <h2>Telehealth Services</h2>
  <p>
    If you need to refill a prescription or discuss medication concerns, please reach out to your clinician. You can submit requests through our client portal or by contacting our office directly.
  </p>

  <h2>Administrative Support</h2>
  <p>
    Our administrative team can assist with:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Insurance questions and billing inquiries</li>
    <li>Obtaining records or documentation letters</li>
    <li>Updating contact and insurance information</li>
    <li>General questions about our services</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Need to Reach Us?</h2>
  <p>
    <a href="https://heatherlcornett.clientsecure.me/contact-widget" target="_blank">Contact our office</a> during business hours for any questions or concerns.
  </p>
